<center><textEffects>May 17District Court - Defendant Lobby No. 3</textEffects></center>
<line>Dhurke:
Nice work, son! We've finally broken through the last obstacle on the road to revolution!
</line><line>Apollo:
Revolution... It just doesn't seem real.
</line><line>Dhurke:
Yes, well, to think you actually defeated the Fighting Phoenix... All I can say is, that's my boy! Hah-ha ha ha ha ha!
</line><line>Apollo:
<textEffects>(Well, Mr. Wright did have his hands tied. Who knows if I'd have won if he'd been able to fight me head-on.)</textEffects>
</line><line>Athena:
