</line><line>Apollo:
...Saved him?
</line><line>Athena:
Yeah, remember what he said? He didn't have to bend the truth anymore, and it was all thanks to you!
</line><line>Apollo:
I don't know about that. <textEffects>(Still, I guess it IS kinda nice to be appreciated.)</textEffects>
</line><line>Trucy:
