Mr. Wright! <textEffects>(What's that look on his face for?)</textEffects>
</line><line>Phoenix:
Oh, Apollo!
</line><line>Apollo:
Um, is everything all right with Ms. Fey?
</line><line>Phoenix:
She's safe... for now.
</line><line>Athena:
Well then, we'd better go save her, quick! Where is she, anyway?
</line><line>Phoenix:
...I'm afraid I have some bad news.
</line><line>Apollo:
Huh?
</line><line>Phoenix:
Maya's... not here in the States. She's still in Khura'in. And she's still being held hostage by the mastermind behind this whole thing.
</line><line>Apollo:
The mastermind?
</line><line>Phoenix:
...That's right. Paul Atishon-Wimperson was nothing more than a pawn. Maya's true abductor is in the Kingdom of Khura'in.
</line><line>Apollo:
Wh-Whaaaaaaaaaaaat?! I-I don't understand, Mr. Wright! What in the world's going on over there?!
</line>
